System Requirements
===================

Stopgap-measure requires pysam, numpy, pandas (0.8 or greater) and python (2.6 or greater).

Installation
============

Unpack the distribution and enter the stopgap-measure directory.
Type: 
	python setup.py install

to install it within the site-packages directory of your python
distribution.


Run from the command line
=========================

run_measure.py, is a runnable script that is a wrapper for measure.py
It's installed in /usr/local/bin/ in Ubuntu

Type:
	run_measure.py -b <bamfile.bam> -f <fastafile>

or:
	run_measure.py --help

for help on the options.


Architecture specific options
=============================

Stopgap-measure has been tested with Python 2.7. 
